---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-100 to-white">
    <Header />
    <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">üßë‚ÄçüöÄ Hello, Astronaut!</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-lg">
        <p class="mb-4">
          Welcome to the official <a href="https://astro.build/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Astro</a> blog
          starter template. This template serves as a lightweight, minimally-styled starting point for anyone looking to
          build a personal website, blog, or portfolio with Astro.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          This template comes with a few integrations already configured in your
          <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">astro.config.mjs</code> file. You can customize your setup with
          <a href="https://astro.build/integrations" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Astro Integrations</a> to
          add tools like Tailwind, React, or Vue to your project.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">Here are a few ideas on how to get started with the template:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Edit this page in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/pages/index.astro</code></li>
          <li>Edit the site header items in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/components/Header.astro</code></li>
          <li>Add your name to the footer in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/components/Footer.astro</code></li>
          <li>Check out the included blog posts in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/content/blog/</code></li>
          <li>Customize the blog post page layout in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Have fun! If you get stuck, remember to <a
            href="https://docs.astro.build/"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">read the docs</a
          > or <a href="https://astro.build/chat" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">join us on Discord</a> to ask
          questions.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Looking for a blog template with a bit more personality? Check out <a
            href="https://github.com/Charca/astro-blog-template"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">astro-blog-template</a
          > by <a href="https://twitter.com/Charca" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Maxi Ferreira</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>